{"n":108,"name":"الكوثر","phonetic":"Al-Kawthar","fr":"L'abondance","type":"meccan","verses":[["إِنَّآ أَعۡطَيۡنَٰكَ ٱلۡكَوۡثَرَ","Nous t'avons certes, accordé l'Abondance","Inna aAAtaynaka alkawthara"],["فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَٱنۡحَرۡ","Accomplis la Salât pour ton Seigneur et sacrifie","Fasalli lirabbika wainhar"],["إِنَّ شَانِئَكَ هُوَ ٱلۡأَبۡتَرُ","Celui qui te hait sera certes, sans postérité","Inna shaniaka huwa alabtaru"]]}